snippet.title: Thank Goodness You're Here! - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Comedy slapformer Thank Goodness You’re Here! is coming to PC, Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4 & PlayStation 5 on August 1st! Thank Goodness You're Here! is an absurd comedy slapformer set in the bizarre Northern English town of Barnsworth. As a traveling salesman, take the time to see the sights and meet the locals, who are very eager to give you a series of increasingly odd jobs… 
Learn more at https://thankgoodness.game
